Privacy policy

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application App Name Atomic Sheep for mobile devices that was created by Developer Leerom. 
The Application will never use any data of the user. the privacy of the user is perfectly safe.

Moreover this game is perfectly suited for children from 3 to 13 years old.

The application will only show few ads to monetize the application creation and maintenance.

Have fun in total security

